title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Native Airbus A330 900neo - version 0.9.0
description:
In this video we will look at the Native Airbus A330-900 Neo which has been recently updated to version 0.9.0. The aircraft has the same cockpit as the A32NX from FBW but if you don't have the FBW version installed no problem because this aircraft has it's own copy. The downside of it is that it is not based on the latest version of the A32NX. After looking from the outside we will shortly look inside and than take off and fly a bit with the aircraft.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/18198/airbus-a330-900neo-conversion
